					<p>The Quorum of the Twelve, April 1921, next to the Salt Lake Temple. Seated: Rudger Clawson (quorum president), Reed Smoot, George Albert Smith, George F. Richards, Orson F. Whitney, David O. McKay; standing: Joseph Fielding Smith, James E. Talmage, Stephen L Richards, Richard R. Lyman, Melvin J. Ballard, John A. Widtsoe (newest member at time of this photograph).</p>
